description:
Any props such as style or event listeners will be applied to the
main floating action button. If you want props applied to the `SpeedDial`
itself, you will need to set them in the `containerProps` prop.

isOpen.description:
A boolean if the speed dial is currently open. This will make
the speed dial into a controlled component.

initiallyOpen.description: Boolean if the uncontrolled speed dial is initially open.

className.description: An optional className to apply to the speed dial.

transitionName.description:
The speed dial's floating action button transition name when the button's
open state changes. If the button is open, `-right` is appened, otherwise
`-left`.

transitionEnterTimeout.description: The timeout for the speed dial's floating action button transition.

speedDialTransitionName.description: The name for the flinging animation of the speed dial.

speedDialTransitionEnterTimeout.description: The timeout for the flinging animation of the speed dial when opening.

speedDialTransitionLeaveTimeout.description: The timeout for the flinging animation when the speed dial is closing.

passiveIconChildren.description: The optional children to display for unopened speed dial floating action button.

passiveIconClassName.description: The optional icon className to display for unopened speed dial floating action button.

activeIconChildren.description: The optional children to display for opened speed dial floating action button.

activeIconClassName.description: The optional icon className to display for opened speed dial floating action button.

type.name: custom

fabs.description:
A list of `FloatingButton` or props to generate the `FloatinButton` when the
`SpeedDial` is open. The buttons will automatically be converted to the `mini`
version.

onClick.description: An optional function to call when the main floating action button is clicked.

onPassiveClick.description: An optional function to call when the main floating action button is clicked.

onActiveClick.description: An optional function to call when the main floating action button is clicked.

containerProps.description: Any additional props to apply to the speed dial itself.
